{"tid":1630959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁蒙面法】網片傳防暴警拳打腳踢一被制服黑衣男","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:11.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3bfdac976e7c7fc2d4571279e3ce99a4fa02c1c9","tid":1630959,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191006/s00001/1570363670065/【禁蒙面法】網片傳防暴警拳打腳踢一被制服黑衣男\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570363670065%2F%E3%80%90%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E7%89%87%E5%82%B3%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%A2%E4%B8%80%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E7%94%B7&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6sZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=e6eb2752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F1570363670065%2F%E3%80%90%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E7%89%87%E5%82%B3%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%A2%E4%B8%80%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E7%94%B7&h=17beaf5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191006/s00001/1570363670065/【禁蒙面法】網片傳防暴警拳打腳踢一被制服黑衣男</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《禁蒙面法》生效第二天，網民號召今午（6日）於港島及九龍遊行，沒申請警方不反對通知書；防暴警察在多區採取驅散及拘捕行動。民陣副召集人陳皓桓在facebook上載片段，顯示有兩名防暴警察對一名已被制服的黑衣男子拳打腳踢。<br />\n<br />\n片段中，有身處較高位置的人見狀，向警方投擲杯裝飲品，又聽到有人大叫「喂，唔好打人啊」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指出，涉事位置為新蒲崗譽．港灣附近。明報網站正就事件詳情向警方查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191006/s00001/4ae2c777937699aa79a3d6f9e1855fcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191006%2Fs00001%2F4ae2c777937699aa79a3d6f9e1855fcb.jpg&h=45f11a14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7df93a65f18e8521ff0a3a233224b198ab5bd6f6","tid":1630959,"uid":27